virtualTable.name: minor-roads-casing
virtualTable.sql: select osm_id, way,highway, case when tunnel in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else 'no' end as tunnel, case when service in ('parking_aisle','drive-through','driveway') then 'INT-minor'::text else service end as service from planet_osm_line where highway in ('motorway','motorway_link','trunk','trunk_link','primary','primary_link','secondary','secondary_link','tertiary','tertiary_link','residential','unclassified','road','service','pedestrian','raceway','living_street') order by z_order
